						               													<description>You are the manager of a futuristic vehicle racing team and must win the hearts of the public assisted by your mechanic robots and your pilot. It is a workers placement with race management and vehicle improvement while managing the chaos of combat between players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In a turn, you have 2 actions. You must move your vehicle and your second action may be to place a worker, make another movement or use your weapon.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The workers have various possibilities like going to get parts to improve your vehicle, entertaining the crowd to increase your glory, repairing your vehicle, stealing parts from other players and many others.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There is a system for hitting between vehicles and hitting robotic workers on the track.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when the first player finishes his third turn on the track. After, each player plays his last round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The final scoring is done by counting the points of glory accumulated in each round, end of game objectives, each point not accumulated counts for half and finally, each 2 pieces count for 1 point.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are several mechanics in this game. There is a part making charter. Glory points are accumulated by interacting with other players and you must also manage the race and the workers placement.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
